snippet.title: X2: Wolverine's Revenge - 2003 Trailer [High Quality]
snippet.description:
High quality trailer of the game X-Men 2: Wolverine's Revenge, released in 2003 for Playstation 2, Xbox, PC and GameCube.

Source: Cube Magazine 1 bonus disc.
